dmca.title: Melby Ranch asserts trademark in name, via DMCA
dmca.body:
Dear User Support:

This firm represents Melby Ranch Properties, LLC, in connection with the protection of its intellectual property. The copyright and trade-mark name Melby Ranch has been infringed. The infringing material is located at ripoffreport.com/reports/ripoff55287.htm.

This following statement is made in accordance with the Digital Millennium Copyright Act ("DMCA"), 17 U.S.C.
